.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, milk, tea
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, aquamarine, mauve, turquise
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, rugby, swimming, tennis
 1. the person who likes mauve is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
 3. the person who's sport is rugby and the person who likes purple have the same parity positions##9
 4. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the right of the person who likes turquise##5
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 7. the person who likes turquise is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
 8. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking milk##2
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
10. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
11. the person who likes purple is not to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##8
12. the person who likes turquise is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
13. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
14. the person who likes mauve is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | 7up   | milk     | tea     |
| Music-Genre   | aquamarine    | purple   | turquise      | mauve    |
| Sport         | tennis   | rugby | swimming | cycling |

