.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, fishing, hiking, video-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, climbing, sailing, rugby
4 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, mouse, turtle
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##8
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere between the person who's sport is rugby and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's sport is cricket have different parity positions##9
 6. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
 7. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 9. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
10. the owner of the bird is between the person who's sport is cricket and the owner of the turtle##2
11. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the person who's sport is cricket##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | video-games | hiking     | drawing  | fishing |
| Nationality   | climbing       | cricket    | sailing | rugby |
| Pet           | mouse       | guinea-pig | bird     | turtle  |

