 7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the cape-cod house is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5
10. the cape-cod house is between the person who's sport is rowing and the farmhouse house##2
11. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |
