 7. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8
 8. the person drinking milk and the person who's sport is badminton have the same parity positions##9
 9. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
11. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's birthday is in march##2
