.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, egyptian, italian
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, lizard, rabbit
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, milk, cola, soy-milk
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 3. the person drinking milk is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
 4. the dutch is on the right of the argentine##1
 5. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 6. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the egyptian##5
 7. the egyptian and the person drinking milk have different parity positions##9
 8. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 9. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person drinking water##1
10. the argentine is not to the right of the dutch##8
11. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person drinking milk##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |
| Nationality   | argentine | dutch    | egyptian   | italian       |
| Pet           | ferret    | lizard   | chinchilla | rabbit        |
| Sport         | soy-milk  | water | cola     | milk |

 